{"tid":1646961,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"請大家錄低自己屋苑個CCTV 救救手足","createTime":"2019-10-11T14:05:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T14:10:13.000Z","uid":186908,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0f6e43c666b7259ff0052e9c4037e6503f5b6f00","tid":1646961,"uid":186908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T14:05:49.000Z","msg":"各位手足，係時候做啲嘢！<br />\n<br />\n越來越多手足被自殺，沉冤待雪。大家可否行多一步？做啲野？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">每晚瞓覺前，開咗你部電視，選定台，監察你座大廈公共地方(尤其大堂)的頻道，然後用手機錄影低。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n第二朝起身快速看看片段，留意當晚有冇異常可疑人物出入。被自殺的手足未必當晚會被行動，可能會放置在大廈內某啲空置單位裏面幾日。<br />\n<br />\n所以呢個行動或多或少可以制止某些事情發生，尤其是住在<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">公屋或者居屋</span></span>的手足們。我相信如果有需要，房署或房委會係會提供空置單位配合黑警行動。<br />\n<br />\n同樣嘅監察亦都可以叫屋企望到海邊嘅手足幫手，愈多人錄影，就愈多手足受到保護。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8db54cba9d95d69efc7b70ca324d3442c47fbcf","tid":1646961,"uid":186908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T14:06:08.000Z","msg":"自推幾下"},{"pid":"b6753ee746b39f45fb94602b7f681899a9080832","tid":1646961,"uid":107649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T14:06:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ac3bf92108a411f2da355deec9950bc5445007fa","tid":1646961,"uid":186908,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T14:07:23.000Z","msg":"屋企有cctv 較下位 對住錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59f4e5834555737ea56811950130d43c7f1644d0","tid":1646961,"uid":107649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T14:07:38.000Z","msg":"屋宛門口加個cam就最好"},{"pid":"b5287bc85831ac93f4906dfe50e127216af4cf24","tid":1646961,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T14:08:08.